# Application Design System Specification

## Core Design Philosophy
- **Theme**: Eco-friendly, Modern, Clean, Data-Centric
- **Visual Style**: Glassmorphism (Frosted Glass), Soft Gradients, Floating Cards
- **Primary Color**: Emerald Green (`#10b981`) representing nature/ecology
- **Interaction**: Smooth transitions, Hover lift effects, Scale animations

## Design Tokens

### Colors
- **Primary (Emerald)**:
  - Main: `#10b981` (Emerald-500)
  - Hover: `#059669` (Emerald-600)
  - Active: `#047857` (Emerald-700)
  - Light/Bg: `#ecfdf5` (Emerald-50), `rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.08)`
  - Gradient: `linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%)`

- **Secondary (Accents)**:
  - Blue: `#3b82f6` (Info/Weather)
  - Purple: `#8b5cf6` (Data/Files)
  - Cyan: `#06b6d4` (Size/Storage)
  - Amber: `#f59e0b` (Processing/Warning)
  - Red: `#ef4444` (Error/Delete)

- **Backgrounds**:
  - **App Base**: `linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f1f5f9 50%, #e2e8f0 100%)`
  - **Glass Panel**: `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7)` with `backdrop-filter: blur(20px)`
  - **Sidebar**: `linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95) 0%, rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.9) 30%, rgba(240, 253, 244, 0.85) 70%, rgba(236, 253, 245, 0.9) 100%)`
  - **Hover State**: `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9)`

- **Typography Colors**:
  - Primary: `#1f2937` (Gray-800)
  - Secondary: `#6b7280` (Gray-500)
  - Tertiary: `#9ca3af` (Gray-400)

### UI Elements

- **Shadows**:
  - Base: `0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04)`
  - Hover: `0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08)`
  - Glow (Primary): `0 4px 20px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15)`
  - Icon Shadow: `0 2px 8px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2)`

- **Borders**:
  - Default: `1px solid rgba(229, 231, 235, 0.4)`
  - Hover: `rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3)`

- **Radius**:
  - Card: `12px` or `16px`
  - Icon Box: `10px` or `12px`
  - Button: `4px` or `8px`

- **Transitions**:
  - Standard: `all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1)`

## Component Patterns

### Dialogs
- **Header**:
  - Background: `linear-gradient(to right, #ecfdf5, #ffffff)`
  - Title Color: `#047857` (Emerald-700)
  - Bottom Border: `1px solid #f0fdf4`
- **Body**: Padding `24px 32px`.
- **Footer**: Top border `1px solid #f3f4f6`, right-aligned buttons.

### Selection Cards (Grid Layout)
- **Container**: Rounded-xl, Border (Gray-200), White bg.
- **Active State**:
  - Background: `rgba(236, 253, 245, 0.9)` (Emerald-50)
  - Border: `1px solid #10b981` (Emerald-500)
  - Shadow: `0 4px 6px -1px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1)`
- **Hover State**: Lift effect (`-translate-y-1`), shadow increase.
- **Icon**: Large (Text-3xl), wrapped in a container with Emerald gradient background when active.

### Cards (Glass Card)
```css
.card {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(229, 231, 235, 0.4);
  border-radius: 16px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.card:hover {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
}

/* Optional Gradient Stripe */
.card::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 4px;
  height: 100%;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #10b981, #059669);
  transform: scaleY(0);
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.card:hover::before {
  transform: scaleY(1);
}
```

### Buttons
```css
/* Primary Button */
.btn-primary {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%); /* Emerald-500 to 600 */
  color: white;
  border: none;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
  transition: all 0.2s;
}

.btn-primary:hover {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #047857 100%); /* Emerald-600 to 700 */
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);
}
```

### Icons
```css
